snippet.title: RUSSIA - THE PRISON OF NATIONS | Telegraphist 1920: Beats of War
snippet.description:
DEMO ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2584510

A rhythm historical game about sending Morse code to the beat in 1920 (Polish-Soviet War).

Join our Discord server: https://discord.com/invite/VmqQyX5Ng7
